snippet.title: Industrial Annihilation - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Support Industrial Annihilation on Kickstarter and unlock incredible digital and physical rewards! https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/indannihilation/133016859 

The next major game in the Planetary Annihilation universe, Industrial Annihilation combines the iconic real-time strategy of the beloved Annihilation games with deep factory-building to deliver a blend of genres unlike any you’ve experienced before.

The galaxy is at stake, Commander. Claim it.
